## Canonical workflow surface

This project is skills-first. Read `.agents/skills/devguard/SKILL.md` before
changing code or governance files. `CLAUDE.md` is the Claude-compatible context
projection; `conventions/README.md` is the single rule authority.

## Required workflow

1. Inspect `STATUS.md` and `docs/plan/开发清单.md` before implementation.
2. Write or update tests before behavior changes.
3. Run `python scripts/devguard.py verify` and focused tests.
4. Keep secrets out of code, logs, fixtures, and commit messages.
5. Record only commands and evidence that actually ran.

Do not create a second rules or commands authority. Add a canonical skill first;
legacy command shims are allowed only when a real harness requires them.
